soot.toolkits.graph

Class SimpleDominatorsAnalysis<N>

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.toolkits.scalar.AbstractFlowAnalysis<N,A>
      • soot.toolkits.scalar.FlowAnalysis<N,A>
        • soot.toolkits.scalar.ForwardFlowAnalysis<N,FlowSet<N>>
          • soot.toolkits.graph.SimpleDominatorsAnalysis<N>

  •  class SimpleDominatorsAnalysis<N>
extends ForwardFlowAnalysis<N,FlowSet<N>>
    Calculate dominators for basic blocks.

    Uses the algorithm contained in Dragon book, pg. 670-1. 

           D(n0) := { n0 }
       for n in N - { n0 } do D(n) := N;
       while changes to any D(n) occur do
         for n in N - {n0} do
             D(n) := {n} U (intersect of D(p) over all predecessors p of n)
